       - `DialogBody className="px-5 custom-scrollbar"` → `className="custom-scrollbar"`
       - `bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200` → `bg-muted/60 border border-border`
       - `text-amber-800` → `text-muted-foreground`
       - `rounded-[10px]` → `rounded-lg` (2 occurrences in loading states)
       - Added `DialogDescription` and `DialogFooter` to import block
     - **Round 2 (unused import cleanup by Front-end-Code)**:
       - Removed: `X as X`, `Search`, `Command`, `CommandEmpty`, `CommandGroup`, `CommandInput`, `CommandItem`, `CommandList`, `Card`, `Separator`, `serviceTasksService`, `UserServiceTask`, `useAssistants` from imports
     - **Round 3 (SelectPopover substitution — IN PROGRESS at summary)**:
       - Import changed: `Select, SelectContent, SelectItem, SelectTrigger, SelectValue` → `SelectPopover`
       - Removed `Input` import (was only used in manual search inside SelectContent)
       - Removed `Search` from lucide imports
       - **Cliente field**:
         ```tsx
         <SelectPopover
           value={selectedClient}
